<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 1.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Bind next to the rogue trainer near the mines entrance. If you see trouble just gate out there, and dare the spiders to come and get hit for 450x4 in one round (I say spiders because they are the only ones that ever forced me to gate).<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 2.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> I managed to push it higher here. I'm not positive, but I think I was coming back here all the way through 41/42 but I know that whichever it was (41 or 42) they were seriously green more than 50% of the time. If I had it to do over again, I would have left and gone to the solo spawn specter in Feerott at 39 instead of messing with it even though at 39 and 40 the exp was still fairly fast if I had the entire bottom of the mines.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 3.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> From in the 5-6 levels I spent here I totaled 30 heads. When I walked out of Thurgaddin for good and into GD I auctioned &quot;Selling coldain heads 100pp each, send tells&quot;. They were gone in less than 2 min and the last guy would have bought more.<br>
<br>
If I ever decide to take another mage through these levels I would definetly visit this place again.<br>
<br>
Good hunting,<br>
