<br>
I parked my pet in the back of the cave beyond the third pit. Nothing wandered there so it was safe to go afk while medding. I used a water pet with all the buffs I could give it. I would pull from the 3-spawn spot back to the cave one or two mobs at a time. I never got stuck with three because of the pathing. If you wait for one to move out into the corridor from the side cave, you can always safely pull only one or two. <br>
<br>
After clearing the 3 spawns, I would look at my watch and med for about 7 minutes. Then I would go clear the 2-spawns by the ladder. If you run off the pit at an angle, you fall into the connecting tunnel and do not get any aggro. So, you can at least get the mobs targeted the way you want to for aggro management purposes. I would then go over to the first pit and look up. You could target one of the mobs standing on top at the edge on either side. After disposing of one of the mobs (there are usually two), I ran back to the farthest cave in the back and medded up for 7 minutes. Then I cleared the 3-spawn spot again. Rinse, repeat, and so forth.<br>
<br>
I did not have the good luck with coldain heads some had though. Only 5 heads in three levels. I'll need to sell them for 100 pp each in order to make this camp monetarily profitable. The experience was awesome though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.showMessageRange?topicID=28.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.showPrevMessage?topicID=28.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.showNextMessage?topicID=28.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=28.topic&index=31><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.threadControl?topicID=28.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=28.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm44.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=28.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstow